City Hall will be lit White, Orange and Green to celebrate Diwali - Festival of Lights.

The Federation of Indian Communities of Queenslnd (FICQ) invites you to Diwali Festival of Lights, King Goerge Square Friday 24 October 2025. Diwali is a joyous celebration observed across India, symbolizing the triumph of good over evil. Traditionally, people showcase their ceativity by fashioning vibrant rangolis with colours or flowers, adorning the streets with lights, lighting diyas, using eco-friendly firecrackers, and sharing gifts, sweets, and savoury treats. This festival serves as a unifying and uplifting experience for communities throughout India.&nbsp;

This Light Up is organised by: Federation of Indian Communities of Qld
